Post: As we continue to support the government‚Äôs efforts to fight against the spread of COVID-19, ALL BRANCHES nationwide will be closed until the end of the ECQ period.  For your convenience, you may use our digital facilities to manage your policies, make payments, and file claims.  Register to Manulife Online to view your policy details and make premium payments: online.manulife.com.ph  Submit claims electronically by emailing the requirements to PHCustomerCare@manulife.com.  Please note that the list of claims requirements is available on the Manulife Philippines website: www.manulife.com.ph For more information, you may call our Customer Care hotline: (02) 8884-7000 from 9am-3pm, Monday - Friday (except holidays). #ManulifeAdvisory
